&lt;li&gt;Operate as the primary people strategy partner to business leaders across all functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring a clear point of view that helps leaders navigate complexity, elevate their impact, and make better decisions—not just HR process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build trusted relationships with executives and senior ICs; become the person they call before a decision, not after.&lt;/li&gt;
