&lt;li&gt;Write clean, maintainable code and build reusable modules to streamline future deployments.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate across cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP) to ensure secure, performant infrastructure.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously improve deployment tools, pipelines, and methodologies to reduce time-to-value.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
