&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job responsibilities :&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and drive the demand and supply growth roadmap in partnership with the Head of Talent Growth.&lt;/li&gt;
